<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
order [target] [command] : order a pet to do something<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
The order command is used to control your pets.  Some pets cannot perform<br>
specific commands; these will vary according to a pet's makeup.<br>
<br>
Some sample commands are sleep, rest, and stand.<br>
<br>
Note: Using order as a means to get past language barriers is against the<br>
rules we have set down.<br>
</html>
</body>
